name: CI Short Term Government Bond Index Class ETF
longDescription: The First Asset Short Term Government Bond Index Class ETF has been designed to replicate to the extent possible the performance of a Canadian short term government bond index currently the FTSE TMX Canada Short Term Government Bond Index net of expenses. Under normal market conditions the First Asset ETF primarily invests in Canadian federal provincial and municipal bonds issued domestically in Canada and denominated in Canadian dollars. The First Asset Short Term Government Bond Index Class ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of a Canadian short term government bond index, currently the FTSE TMX Canada Short Term Government Bond Index, net of expenses. Under normal market conditions, the First Asset ETF primarily invests in Canadian federal, provincial and municipal bonds issued domestically in Canada and denominated in Canadian dollars.
